# ─── CityLens Environment Variables ───────────────────
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your API keys.
# The frontend (Vite) reads VITE_* vars, the backend reads the rest via python-dotenv.

# Gemini API Key — used by BOTH frontend and backend
# Frontend reads:  VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY  (via import.meta.env)
# Backend reads:   GEMINI_API_KEY       (via os.getenv after load_dotenv)
